OL,3,CGatland to step down mid-way through
OL,4,CSix Nations
OL,6,FWarren Gatland will leave his role as
OL,7,Fhead coach of Wales today, ITV Wales
OL,8,Funderstands.
OL,10,FITV Wales understands that Cardiff
OL,11,FRugby head coach Matt Sherratt has
OL,12,Fbeen lined up to replace Gatland on an
OL,13,Finterim basis until the end of the Six
OL,14,FNations.
OL,16,FFor months, his job has been under
OL,17,Fthreat amid a record run of defeats
OL,18,Fbut the WRU decided to keep him in
OL,19,Fpost after a winless 2024.
