OL,3,CGatland to step down mid-way through
OL,4,CSix Nations
OL,6,FThe Kiwi returned to Wales after a
OL,7,Fhugely-successful first stint in
OL,8,Fcharge between 2008 and 2019. The run
OL,9,Fincluded multiple Grand Slams, World
OL,10,FCup semi-finals, a record run of
OL,11,Fvictories and a brief stint as World
OL,12,FNo.1.
OL,14,FHe was brought back to rescue
OL,15,Fpreparations for the 2023 Rugby World
OL,16,FCup, which were going off the rails.
